uk.gov.nationalarchives.droid.base
Class DroidConstants

java.lang.Object
  uk.gov.nationalarchives.droid.base.DroidConstants

public class DroidConstants
extends Object

Controls the file format identification analysis On startup, it launches either the command line or the GUI package. It then exposes the necessary methods for running the file identification analysis.
